title: CMU EDA Project
text:
This is my EDA Project completed during my REU at Carnegie Mellon University. This was collaboration project with Olivia Kim and Arturo Espana. An Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) project involves systematically examining a dataset to understand its main characteristics, identify patterns, and potentially uncover insights before formal analysis or modeling. We built an analysis on the shipment and delivery of COVID-19 Vaccinations in counties throughout California
